 400:fips202.c     **** *              - size_t nblocks: number of blocks to be squeezed (written to h)
 401:fips202.c     **** *              - uint64_t *s: pointer to input/output Keccak state
 402:fips202.c     **** *              - unsigned int r: rate in bytes (e.g., 168 for SHAKE128)
